long_desc.thetext:
qooxdoo had a license header:

/** qooxdoo v4.0 | (c) 2015 1&1 Internet AG, http://1und1.de | http://qooxdoo.org/license */

This should be added for the grunt toolchain, too. I would add the git rev too, because then it's reproducible (which is crucially for next anyway, because we don't have releases yet). For example:


/** next 4.1 (rev 831ab86) | (c) 2015 1&1 Internet AG, http://1und1.de | http://qooxdoo.org/license */
